&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“Who do you think will feel sorry for you, Jerusalem? Who do you think will waste tears on you? Who will bother to take the time to ask, ‘So, how are things going?’, You left me, remember?” GOD ’s Decree. (Jeremiah 15:5-6 MSG)&lt;/p&gt;
